Description: GitHub PR Review and Merge Script
 A comprehensive bash script for reviewing and merging GitHub Pull Requests
 using the GitHub CLI. This script streamlines the PR workflow by combining
 review approval and merge operations into a single command.
 .
 Features include safety checks, interactive and auto modes, multiple merge
 methods, and comprehensive error handling.
